===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=刚}} 
Along with {{och-l|鋼|steel}}, derived from the terminative of {{och-l|固|firm, solid, hard}}, literally "having become solid, hard" ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). The word can be reconstructed all the way back to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*rkaŋ}}.

